column45: Mostly just in the last year or so, because I moved to a new house and had a REALLY tough time with it because I'm so bad with change, so I started doing more research on ASD and reconsidering my own experiences. Like I always thought I couldn't be autistic because I don't experience a lack of empathy, but then I learned that's just a stereotype and you can also experience hyper-empathy with autism, so now I'm really wondering if I have it since I get overwhelmed by other people's emotions. But I don't know anything for sure.
